node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Girl and Her Moon ☾ on September 07, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'Life is calling us to step forward and declare who we are, who we desire to be, and the life we desire to create. girl and her moon'.

node.text:
Life is supporting each of us so deeply right now, whispering it's beautiful guidance.

This New Moon is awakening us to what is important, what truly matters.

It is asking us to open our eyes to the path we are on, and the path we desire to intentionally walk on.

Like a bursting seed, there is new life in motion.

There is this deep feeling of importance to connect within right now.

A Soul call to step forward and declare who we are, who we desire to be, and the life we desire to create.

A Soul call to to declare, own, be the strength that we are, be the divine creators of our life.

Tarot is one of the many tools we use to bring a deep awareness to the energies in our life, what they are saying specifically to you.

It is a tool that represents the change ready to happen.

It mirrors the new life that is ready and willing to burst open, once we say yes.

Tarot is a way for us to take charge of the path we are walking on.

We'd love to invite you to step forward with us on this beautiful New Moon.

And say yes to this new blooming of you.

In whatever way we can support you. 

Tarot, Astrology, Soul Work.

You can find all of our offerings via the link in our bio. 🖤

For members - make sure you are logged in here to receive your discount. 🦋

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Girl and Her Moon ☾ on September 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'New Mon Ritual CLABORATION With Breathwork facilitator Tanya Saunders embodiment & breath Virgo New Moon Healing Breathwork Session GIRLANDHERM'.

node.text:
VIRGO NEW MOON RITUAL: EMBODIMENT & BREATH ✨

Virgo New Moon Healing Breathwork Session with @tanya_saunders_ – an exclusive ritual to our Flow with the Moon Membership.

This breathwork session is designed to align with the energy of Virgo.

To clear energy. To move energy.

To reorganise energy. To ground.

To restore health and balance. To refine our intentions, our motives.

To remember and return to the truth of what and who we desire to be, to bring clarity to how we desire to live.

To manifest. To dream bigger.

To step forward. To start anew.

Pre-recorded to move through in your own safe space, and aligned time, you will have lifelong access to this recording.

Join us under this New Moon to embody the beautiful energy of this beautiful New Moon.

The recording will be available instantly upon signing up.

Find out more about the Flow with the Moon Membership via the link in our bio. 🖤

node.text:
Stepping into September…♡

This month whispers a flow of transition, of change, of a clearing and reorganisation.
 
Of highlighting our priorities and stripping away the rest. 

Of reflection – a sacred ‘pause’ where we are guided to look around at our lives, look within at who we are, review our course, and decide if we are heading in a direction we desire.
 
Stepping into the month we have the Sun in Virgo.

Virgo reorganises. It is deeply healing, able to place things in their most optimal spaces.

Able to see what is in alignment, and what is ready to fall away.

Being a mutable energy, it speaks to adaptability, flexibility, transition.
 
With our beautiful New Moon in Virgo and an emotional and healing Pisces Full Moon, this month also holds a beautiful event – the September Equinox.

The official halfway point of the astrological year and a harmonious shift in energy as the Sun moves into Libra.
 
Reaching the end of September, we meet the last  Mercury Retrograde of 2021, bringing us to a total of 6 planets in retrograde for a moment.

This cosmic line up of our beautiful planets moving in a retrograde emphasises that sacred pause, reflection, introspection, and review of our lives.

With the numerology of both 5 and 9, this shows us both changes in direction and endings of a cycle. 

✧

September’s full energetic report can be found inside our Flow with the Moon Membership.

With the key astrological transits of the month and their dates, with a dive into each New and Full Moon, and an in-depth tarot reading covering the energy.

This month inside of the membership, we have a New Moon Ritual with the beautiful @tanya_saunders_ – a healing breathwork session.

And a beautiful, nurturing, energy rich Soul Journey for the Full Moon, Healing with Light.

We also dive into the final Mercury Retrograde of 2021, and the beautiful September Equinox.

Along with a beautiful tarot reading for the month, intention setting, soul prompts, gratitude work and more.

To find out more, or to take the step and join this beautiful space alongside over 1200 other women, the link can be found in our bio. 💖

node.text:
Let yourself feel supported.⁣
⁣
Remind yourself of the abundance in this life.⁣
⁣
The way that flowers bloom so magically.⁣
⁣
Trees that have seen more than we could dream of seeing in one lifetime.⁣
⁣
The people creating deep impact in this world.⁣
⁣
The infinite amount of stars that exist.⁣
⁣
The sparkle in ones eyes as they tap into their passion.⁣
⁣
Every single time you have laughed, felt joy flowing through your body, and experienced the beauty of love.⁣
⁣
There is more than enough for you, in this moment and every single moment to come.⁣
⁣
There is magic waiting to be witnessed by you.⁣
⁣
Magic waiting for permission to flow freely into your life.⁣
⁣
There is your heart bursting with dreams and unlimited possibilities waiting to be explored.⁣
⁣
Life is abundant. You are abundant.⁣
⁣
Abundant in flow, ease, joy, love, experiences, adventure, creativity, money, dreams, connection.⁣
⁣
Abundant in whatever you desire to be abundant in – it is available.⁣
⁣
Tap into this abundance by witnessing all that already exists in this incredible life.⁣
⁣
 🤍
